  "context_for_next_testing_agent": "Iteration 5 features tested and verified: PDF Generation (Invoice and Capability Brochure using jsPDF with autoTable), Website Integration page with WordPress link and marketing materials, Google Drive Sync page (MOCKED - demo mode). Two bugs were fixed: 1) G-Drive router had duplicate /api prefix, 2) jspdf-autotable 5.0 requires new import syntax.",
